            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Last night I tried Hitachino Nest Japanese Classic Ale by <a href="http://www.kodawari.cc/?en_home/products/hitachino-nest-beer.html" class="postlink" rel="nofollow">Kiuchi Brewery</a>. It's a pale ale that is aged in cedar casks, and the hop and cedar flavors harmonize beautifully. I loved it, and will buy it again.

              

              
              
            </div>
